Sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: Before experiment, the MCF7 cells were hormone-stripped in phenol red-free DMEM medium plus 5% charcoal-treated FBS for 3 days, followed by treatemnt of either 100 nM 17β-estrodial (E2) or ethanol as vehcile control for 1hr.
Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: MCF7 obtained from ATCC were cultured in DMEM media supplemented with 10% FBS in a 5% CO2 humidified incubator at 37°C.
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Lysates were clarified from sonicated nuclei and protein-DNA complexes were isolated with antibody., The extracted ChIP DNA was ligated to specific adaptors using  KAPA Hyper Prep Kit (KK8504), according to the manufacturer’s instructions.
Sample_data_processing: Basecalls performed using Illuminal CASAVA software., ChIP-seq reads were aligned to the hg19 genome assembly using bowtie v1.1.2 with only uniquely mapped reads retained., Peaks were called using MACS2 with q-value less than 1e-5. The peaks overlapped with the blacklist regions downloaded from UCSC were removed
Sample_contact_institute: Universality of Texas Health Science Center at San Antonio
